data.description:
Prime Location! Views into Glacier National Park. Your Montana adventure begins here in the North Fork, with two homes situated on a generous 2.5-acre corner lot. This property is very close to GNP, river access, warm spring lakes and a short drive to Whitefish ski resort. Ski, mountain bike and hike right from home on miles of National Forest trails. Vacation where you live with the added income of a successful rental property included. Seclusion and scenery with panoramic views of towering trees, lush woods, and mountains. Backs to National Forest and is on the school bus route. Easy access to hiking, fishing, rafting, alpine skiing, cross country, wildlife and more. Main Home (2820 sqft): The main home boasts three generously-sized bedrooms and two full bathrooms. Spacious dine in kitchen with all appliances included. High-speed internet, and a dedicated theatre/media room offers the perfect escape for movie nights and entertainment. Guest Home (1064 sq ft): The second home, a charming 2-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom haven, has not only served as a peaceful retreat but also as a successful nightly rental, providing the opportunity for an additional income stream. It comes equipped with all appliances, private deck and patio, ready to offer family or guests a cozy and unforgettable stay. This has been a favorite VRBO home since 2012. It is also handicap-accessible and ADA compliant. 
Garage and Workshop (1120 sq ft): For those in need of ample storage space, the detached garage features a workshop area and gym, and offers 1120 square feet of possibilities including a living space loft with a finished bedroom.  Also started and ready for you to finish is a bathroom, electric & rough plumbed for kitchen/bath, as well as washer/dryer hook-ups.
Whether you are sipping your morning coffee on the porch enjoying the wildlife, or embarking on outdoor adventures right from your doorstep and exploring the wonders of the Flathead National Forest that backs this property, Flathead River, and Glacier National Park (West Entrance) just 12 minutes away, you will feel like you have come home to Montana.
